OL,7,FCivil war has torn apart Sudan for
OL,8,Fprecisely two years, we hear from
OL,9,FSudanese children inside the country
OL,10,Fand from a British doctor who has just
OL,11,Freturned from what he called a scale
OL,12,Fof suffering beyond any other. ITV
OL,13,FNews International Affairs Analyst
OL,14,FRageh Omaar reports, produced by Roohi
OL,15,FHasan
OL,17,FTwo years ago, I was there as the most
OL,18,Frecent conflict in Sudan began, and
OL,19,Fwesterners were urgently evacuated
OL,20,Ffrom its capital city ` Khartoum.
