OL,7,FThey said Sudan has the largest scale
OL,8,Fhunger crisis, the largest
OL,9,Fdisplacement crisis and the largest
OL,10,Fchild protection crisis on the planet.
OL,12,FGetting information out of Sudan or
OL,13,Ffilming there is incredibly
OL,14,Fchallenging and to do this
OL,15,Finvestigation, it took ITV News three
OL,16,Fmonths assisted by filming from NGOs
OL,17,Fincluding UNICEF and MSF.
OL,19,FITV News International Affairs Analyst
OL,20,FRageh Omaar explains the difficulties
OL,21,Fof getting aid into Sudan
