OL,7,FLargest global hunger crisis
OL,9,FThe UN says half the population, 25
OL,10,Fmillion people, are facing acute
OL,11,Fhunger.
OL,13,FThey say hunger has tripled since war
OL,14,Fbroke out, and it is now catastrophic
OL,15,Fin ten out of 18 states.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
