OL,7,FFamine has been declared in not just
OL,8,Fone, but ten areas of a country eight
OL,9,Ftimes the size of the UK, according to
OL,10,Fthe organisation, and the number of
OL,11,Fareas hit is growing, as 17 are now on
OL,12,Fthe brink of famine.
OL,14,FEmergency doctor Dr Javid Abdelmoneim
OL,15,Frecounted to ITV News the desperate
OL,16,Fsituation he witnessed in Sudan
OL,18,FDr Javid Abdelmoneim is an emergency
OL,19,Fmedicine specialist for Medecins Sans
OL,20,FFrontieres, and has worked in conflict
OL,21,Fzones for the past 15 years.
