OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News after his return
OL,8,Ffrom Sudan, Dr Abdelmoneim said:
OL,9,F"There's already been famine declared,
OL,10,Fimagine how much worse it's going to
OL,11,Fget.
OL,13,F"In our own campaigns, we've done
OL,14,Fscreening for malnutrition in Darfur,
OL,15,Fin Omdurman and in the east. And our
OL,16,Frates were between 7% and over 30% of
OL,17,Facute severe malnutrition or global
OL,18,Facute malnutrition. Those are
OL,19,Fstaggering figures."
OL,21,FLargest global displacement crisis
