OL,7,FThe word displacement doesn't do
OL,8,Fjustice to the uprooting of Sudan's
OL,9,Fpopulation.
OL,11,FNine million Sudanese people have been
OL,12,Fdriven from their homes across the
OL,13,Fcountry in just the past 24 months,
OL,14,Fequal to the entire total population
OL,15,Fof London.
OL,17,FMore than half of those 9 million are
OL,18,Fchildren, meaning one child is being
OL,19,Fdisplaced every ten seconds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
