OL,7,FWe spoke to displaced 15-year-old
OL,8,FNahid Ahmed Abdukar, from the Abuja
OL,9,FCamp in Al-Fasher.
OL,11,F"Before the war, I lived a peaceful
OL,12,Flife filled with dreams and
OL,13,Faspirations," she said.
OL,15,F"I was preparing for my high school
OL,16,Fexams when the conflict erupted,
OL,17,Fforcing schools to close. The war
OL,18,Fshattered my morale and spirit," she
OL,19,Fadded.
