OL,7,FThis is a very difficult subject to
OL,8,Fget direct evidence on in any society,
OL,9,Flet alone one where access to victims
OL,10,Fis extremely difficult and where all
OL,11,Fsides to the conflict make it
OL,12,Fdifficult.
OL,14,FHowever, experts warn it is yet
OL,15,Fanother hallmark of what makes Sudan a
OL,16,Ftragedy, which is hard to report and
OL,17,Ftherefore easier to ignore.
