OL,7,FA recent UN report by UNICEF found
OL,8,Fchildren as young as one have been
OL,9,Fvictims of rape. They recorded more
OL,10,Fthan 200 cases of rape against
OL,11,Fchildren aged one to five, affecting
OL,12,Fboth girls and boys.
OL,14,FSheldon Yett, head of UNICEF Sudan,
OL,15,Fshares with ITV News the harrowing
OL,16,Fcases of sexual violence against
OL,17,Fchildren
