OL,7,F"We need to ensure that we hold
OL,8,Fparties accountable and that these
OL,9,Fchildren get the support they
OL,10,Frequire," he added.
OL,12,FUK Government pledges support
OL,14,FThis all comes as the government today
OL,15,Fannounced a #120 million food and aid
OL,16,Fpackage at a conference in London.
OL,18,FOpening the summit, Foreign Secretary
OL,19,FDavid Lammy said it was "morally
OL,20,Fwrong" that "many have given up on
OL,21,FSudan".
