OL,7,FMr Lammy said "with over four million
OL,8,Frefugees having fled the country and
OL,9,Finstability spreading far beyond
OL,10,FSudan's borders, it's also
OL,11,Fstrategically wrong to forget Sudan."
OL,13,F"And that's why, as foreign secretary,
OL,14,FI refuse to turn away. I felt a duty
OL,15,Fto confront this war's horrors head
OL,16,Fon."
