OL,7,FThe summit, co-hosted by the UK
OL,8,Falongside the African Union, the
OL,9,FEuropean Union, France and Germany,
OL,10,Fwas attended by representatives from
OL,11,Fcountries including South Sudan, Saudi
OL,12,FArabia and the US.
OL,14,FMr Lammy told the conference that
OL,15,F"patient diplomacy" was needed to
OL,16,F"relieve the suffering and to end this
OL,17,Fawful war."
