OL,7,F"We cannot be back here one year from
OL,8,Fnow having the same discussion. So
OL,9,Ftoday let's show them and the world
OL,10,Fthat we've not given up on them. We've
OL,11,Fnot given up on Sudan."
OL,13,FThe new #120 million funding aims to
OL,14,Freach more than 600,000 people, with
OL,15,Fthe money going towards supplying
OL,16,Fpulses, oils, salts and cereals to the
OL,17,Fvulnerable.
OL,19,FIt will also help provide emergency
OL,20,Fsupport to survivors of sexual
OL,21,Fviolence.
